  "content": "        <div class=\"bar-fill\" style=\"width: 95%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(139,92,246,0.4), rgba(139,92,246,0.8));\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"bar-value\" style=\"color: var(--accent-purple);\">53 ms</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <!-- Long texts -->\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 12px;\">Long Texts (paragraphs &times; 3)</div>\n    <div class=\"bar-row\">\n      <div class=\"bar-label\" style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">CPU</div>\n      <div class=\"bar-track\">\n        <div class=\"bar-fill\" style=\"width: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(245,158,11,0.3), rgba(245,158,11,0.6));\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"bar-value\" style=\"color: var(--accent-amber);\">56 ms</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"bar-row\">\n      <div class=\"bar-label\" style=\"color: var(--accent-cyan);\">Intel iGPU</div>\n      <div class=\"bar-track\">\n        <div class=\"bar-fill\" style=\"width: 91%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(6,182,212,0.4), rgba(6,182,212,0.8));\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"bar-value\" style=\"color: var(--accent-cyan);\">51 ms</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"bar-row\">\n      <div class=\"bar-label\" style=\"color: var(--accent-purple);\">NVIDIA dGPU</div>\n      <div class=\"bar-track\">\n        <div class=\"bar-fill\" style=\"width: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(139,92,246,0.4), rgba(139,92,246,0.8));\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"bar-value\" style=\"color: var(--accent-purple);\">57 ms</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"insight-box\">\n    <p>For medium and long texts, all three are within ~6ms of each other. The real gap only shows on short-text batches — and that's a CPU startup cost, not a sustained difference.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">04 / 08</div>\n</div>",
